### 🟢 Step 4: (Optional) Deploy on Streamlit Cloud

1. Go to [https://streamlit.io/cloud](https://streamlit.io/cloud)
2. Click **"Sign in with GitHub"**
3. Click **“New App”**
4. Choose:
   - **Repository**: `cybersecurity-anomaly-detector`
   - **Branch**: `main`
   - **Main file path**: `cybersecurity_anomaly_detector.py`
5. Click **"Deploy"**

🔗 Your app will be live in ~30 seconds!

